# OpenCode local install artifacts.
# Both `opencode.json` (plugin pin, mcp.nx, default_agent, and optional per-agent
# model overrides) and the `.opencode/` directory are produced by `opencode-nexus
# install` and `opencode-nexus models` — they are machine-written install outputs,
# not hand-maintained source. Per-agent model picks in particular are personal
# (provider-specific) preferences that must not be forced on other contributors.
# Run `bun run bootstrap` after cloning to regenerate, then use
# `opencode-nexus models` for personal model selection.
opencode.json
.opencode/node_modules
.opencode/package.json
.opencode/package-lock.json
.opencode/bun.lock
.opencode/skills
